{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_05_01",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 05 01",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――NEXT VENUSグランプリ終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "endTime": 2.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 2.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……アイドルに必要なのは物語だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Idols need a story.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.1,
      "endTime": 5.833333333400001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それは輝かしいステージの上でしか語ることは出来ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It can only be told on a dazzling stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.1333333333,
      "endTime": 10.626304086000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 10.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "え？ あっ、はい……\n今、なんて……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Oh‚ yes…\nWhat did you just…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8333333333,
      "endTime": 15.1333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……なんでもない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…It's nothing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4666666667,
      "endTime": 16.8155436167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "急に誘って、悪かったな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for calling you out so suddenly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.82,
      "endTime": 18.853333333400002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 19.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "びっくりしましたけど……\nい、いえ、連絡をいただいた時は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was surprised‚ but…\nN-No‚ when I received your message‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.1666666667,
      "endTime": 23.843975879600002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 24.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "どうしても今日しか時間が取れなくてな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I only had time today‚ you see.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.0333333333,
      "endTime": 26.999999999899998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "社長なんてやるもんじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being a president is not a good thing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27,
      "endTime": 28.9216778315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "三枝がバンプロを辞めたのは、正解だったのかもしれん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe Saegusa was right to leave Van Production.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.6666666667,
      "endTime": 33.7588209788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 34.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "……社長らしくないですね\nそんな弱音を吐くなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's unlike you‚ President.\nTo complain like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.3333333333,
      "endTime": 38.798458199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……そうだな、今のは忘れてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You're right‚ forget what I just said.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.6,
      "endTime": 42.7338549137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 42.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "……いえ、私こそ失礼しました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ I apologize for my rudeness.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.9333333333,
      "endTime": 46.5696599324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ふっ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chuckle …",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.1333333333,
      "endTime": 47.9024262984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 48.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "？ なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "? What is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.1,
      "endTime": 50.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 50.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "母親に随分似てきたと思ってな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought you've become quite like your mother.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.7333333333,
      "endTime": 53.833333333300004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "外見も、中身も",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Both in appearance and personality.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8333333333,
      "endTime": 55.9860242101,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "社長……母のこと……\n……あの、母とは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "President… About my mother…\n…Um‚ my mother and I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.2,
      "endTime": 62.575883107100005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage02",
      "startTime": 62.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "朝倉恭一",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kyoichi",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……予約した店に遅れる。行くぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…We'll be late for our reservation. Let's go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.8,
      "endTime": 65.28585038189999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "……はい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.4666666667,
      "endTime": 67.44631196969999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 68.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 68.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "――と、いうことがあったのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――That's what happened.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5666666667,
      "endTime": 71.9814058463,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 72.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "あの社長が、瑠依ちゃん誘って食事なんて\n初めてなんちゃう！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That president‚ inviting Rui-chan out for a meal…\nIt's the first time‚ isn't it!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.1666666667,
      "endTime": 76.775909018,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 76.9666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "うん、初めて\n私、緊張して、フォーク落としそうになっちゃった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it's the first time.\nI was so nervous‚ I almost dropped my fork.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9666666667,
      "endTime": 82.4521837663,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 82.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "しかも、瑠依ちゃんのお母さんのこと\n話してくれたの初めてなんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And he even talked about your mother‚ Rui-chan‚\nfor the first time‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.6666666667,
      "endTime": 87.64736987600001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "これはすっごい進展だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is huge progress!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.8666666667,
      "endTime": 90.5060316722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 90.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "せやな～、まだぎこちない感じやけど\n大きな前進や",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right~‚ it's still a bit awkward‚\nbut it's a big step forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7,
      "endTime": 96.0045844114,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 96.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "良かったね、瑠依ちゃん！\n次は、勇気を出してお父さんって呼んでみようよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's great‚ Rui-chan!\nNext time‚ try calling him \"Dad\"!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.2333333333,
      "endTime": 102.5596506838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 102.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？ そっ、それは無理よ！\nまだ無理、絶対に無理！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? T-That's impossible!\nIt's still impossible‚ absolutely impossible!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.8666666667,
      "endTime": 107.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanrui-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage03",
      "startTime": 107.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、父親である社長さんの方から\n歩み寄ってきてくれたんやから。次は瑠依ちゃんの番や",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ since your father‚ the president‚\nhas taken a step forward‚ it's your turn‚ Rui-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.9,
      "endTime": 115.39379834329999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_05_01-yu004.m4a",
